{"tid":366722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"The city is not dead yet.","createTime":"2017-08-20T08:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T01:31:20.000Z","uid":134706,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5dde311971bc4d0d859291a7f15396fc12301ab","tid":366722,"uid":134706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"當一個城市的政府不再聽取民眾意見時<br />\n當一個城市的法律制度不再為正義申張時<br />\n當一個城市的核心價值已被侵蝕時<br />\n當一個城市的市民不再為自由奮鬥時<br />\n當一個城市不再有價值時<br />\n當香港淪陷時 就已經不是<br />\nThe city is dying<br />\n而是<br />\nThe city is dead<br />\n<br />\n當我們不再擁有希望時 我們都有責任去保護我們的香港 <br />\n做人做狗 自己諗<br />\n我就出左黎 保護返我地既城市 我地既自由<br />\n各位請堅持 唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\n因為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>The city is not dead yet.</strong></span>"},{"pid":"04351d411c84aad147193d4b710e9e8db8c0862f","tid":366722,"uid":134706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88246b560139f9ac3290ce21f0cd9476ef07c65","tid":366722,"uid":134706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d97a60bb1239daa98503766947819fdb15c802d","tid":366722,"uid":134706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15a39b10e16db875a20129d5d2ae555f77282f3","tid":366722,"uid":134706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d225c5e0b7c25922cd13abd74563e3cb4d7afe","tid":366722,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:15:32.000Z","msg"